					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="push-50 text-justify">
					<h3 class="h5 font-w600 text-uppercase push-5">
						<i class="far fa-money-bill-alt text-flat push-5-r"></i> 100% Free
					</h3>
					<p>Honybot won't cost you a dime and never will.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-2 visible-lg">
				<img class="img-responsive" src="/images/landing/honypromo2.jpg"
